 integration, data engineering, analytics and visualization, cloud platforms, and DevOps and shift left testing services; and embedded product and systems engineering services comprising system, software and hardware, tooling, testing, and consulting services. In addition, the company offers mechanical product engineering services, including new product design and development, value engineering, virtual simulation, and manufacturing engineering. It operates in India, the United States, Europe, Canada, and the United Kingdom. Onward Technologies Limited was incorporated in 1991 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}